## Query Options

**Filtering :** `?column[operator]=value` 

```bash
curl -g "{{$ApiURL}}/products:list?quantity[gt]=100&brand[eq]=Wow" | jq .
```

**Operators:** `eq`, `ne`, `gt`, `lt`, `gte`, `lte`, `like`, `in`

**Sorting :** `?sort={-field1,field2}` 

```bash
curl {{$ApiURL}}/products:list?sort=-quantity,title | jq .
```

Sort by `field` (ascending) or `-field` (descending)

**Full-Text Search :** `?q={search_term}` (across all text columns)

```bash
curl {{$ApiURL}}/products:list?q=mouse | jq .
```

**Field Selection :** `?fields={field1,field2}`

```bash
curl {{$ApiURL}}/products:list?fields=quantity,title | jq .
```

**Limit :** `?limit={limit}`

```bash
curl {{$ApiURL}}/products:list?limit=2 | jq .
```

**Pagination :** `?after={cursor}` (Response includes `next_cursor` when more results are available.)

```bash
curl {{$ApiURL}}/products:list?after=01ARZ3NDEKTSV4RRFFQ69G5FBX&limit=10 | jq .
```

